{"lemma":"حُبْلَيَيْنِ","slug":"حُبْلَيَيْنِ","root":"ح.ب.ل","root_slug":"ح-ب-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ب-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6974"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8F%D8%A8%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92%D9%86%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"pregnant"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ħub.laː/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6974","headword_ar":"حُبْلَى","root":"Hbl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pregnant;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAbilapN","text_ar":"حَابِلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabolaAnapN","text_ar":"حَبْلَانَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also occurs in the same sense: (ISd, K) applied to a woman, (S, Mgh,) or, accord. to AZ, to any animal having a nail, (S,) or to any beast, as, for instance, a sheep, or goat, and a cat: (Msb:) pl. of the first"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabaAlaY","text_ar":"حَبَالَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HubolayaAtN","text_ar":"حُبْلَيَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabaAlayaAtN","text_ar":"حَبَالَيَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) which last is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabaAlaY","text_ar":"حَبَالَى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAbilapN","text_ar":"حَابِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabalapN","text_ar":"حَبَلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which is extr. (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~ayolu HubolaY lasota tadoriY","text_ar":"اللَّيْلُ حُبْلَى لَسْتَ تَدْرِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA talidu","text_ar":"مَا تَلِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The night is pregnant: thou knowest not what it will bring forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: meaning that the events of the night are not to be trusted. (TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabolaAnapN","text_ar":"حَبْلَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["ISd","K","S","Mgh","Msb","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}